c: 6
v: 19
t: "Ini: \"anda p ccada sennig akw tiyav\"? Ini: \"Öebbi d Anagi gari yidwen. Iweêêa yi d Leqwôan agi, iwakken a kwen nabi$ yis, kunwi akked wid u$uô ibbwev. Day, kunwi, war ccekk, a pcehhdem ar, ar tama n Öebbi, llan iôebbiten nniven\"? Ini: \"ur cehhde$\"! Ini: \"Neppa d Öebbi, siwa Yiwen. Nek, rri$ akin ayen tepcarakem"